twcore.core.events
Class InterProcessEvent

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.events.SubspaceEvent
      twcore.core.events.InterProcessEvent

public class InterProcessEvent
extends SubspaceEvent

Event class of the Inter-process Communication protocol of TWCore. Bots may request this event if they intend to send and receive IPC messages.

Author:
harvey
